snippet.title: ULTROS - Narrated Gameplay Preview
snippet.description:
Get a narrated, closer look at the colorful innards of The Sarcophagus. We also present you with a taste of the Tenebra Caligarum – a tool used by the Berian shamasal in their cleansing rituals. It is more popularly known as an Extractor, and its many utility programs will help any sojourner trying to explore the alien landscapes of our drifting space station.

Coming to PS5, PS4 and PC on February 13th, pre-order now!
PlayStation Store: https://store.playstation.com/sv-se/concept/10003373/
Steam: https://bit.ly/3qSwEtQ
Epic Games Store: https://store.epicgames.com/p/ultros
